  "notes": "Born 1520 in Epping, Essex, England. Married Joane Graygoose (1520-1579). Daughter: Alice Benton (1544-1605), who married Francis Rogers and was mother of Sir Robert Rogers. Wife Joane died October 27, 1579 in St Leonard Shoreditch, Middlesex. Humphrey died just 2 days later on October 29, 1579 in Epping — dying within 48 hours of his wife."
